  Separation of Concerns  
    Separation of Concerns 

    Enables mastering of inherent complexity  Allows concentration on individual aspects  Product features  Process features  Economics and management    Concerns may be separated by  time (process sequence)  qualities (e.g., correctness vs. performance)  views to be analyzed separately (data vs. control)  components    Leads to separation of responsibility     
 
   

